data.description: A cute 2 bedroom, 1 bath ranch home with an large 2.5 car garage. It includes a large partially fenced yard with a fire pit and storage shed. Inside we have an open living room and kitchen area. A good size primary bedroom with a large closet. A newer bathroom and utility room with washer and dryer that remain. Also included are kitchen appliances. Close to I-65 shopping and restaurants! Bring an Offer!
